name: Tifa Lockhart's classic outfit by Corneo
description:
This is a textual inversion embedding for Tifa's outfit from classic Final Fantasy VII (not Remake). The embedding will lean towards characters appearing like Tifa but can be overridden with other tags to change how the character looks.

The embedding was trained on NAI so will work best with NAI-based models. The example images were generated with Anything v3.

If you want even more Tifa outfits, I've an embedding for her refined purple dress too https://civitai.com/models/4122/tifas-purple-refined-dress-embedding-by-corneo

Version 2 examples generated with my 7th Heaven Mix https://civitai.com/models/4669/corneos-7th-heaven-mix

Check out my other civitai models for more characters and sex positions! https://civitai.com/user/Master_Corneo

If you enjoy this embed, I genuinely love seeing your creations with it - you can attach them to a review if you're not aware (but not comments sadly)!

modelVersions.description: A version 2 update as with my other models as I discovered a problem in my training data. Remember this is aimed at the outfit, not Tifa as a character, so the improvements here are things like the suspenders being more consistent and the pencil skirt not being quite so wildly short.
